Function Get-System_WSAPI 
{
  <#
   
  .SYNOPSIS	
	Retrieve informations about the array.
  
  .DESCRIPTION
	Retrieve informations about the array.
        
  .EXAMPLE
	Get-System_WSAPI
	Retrieve informations about the array.

  .PARAMETER WsapiConnection 
    WSAPI Connection object created with Connection command	
	
  .Notes
